imdb.plot outline: See the backstage prep of music concerts and what goes into the recording of a new song like you've never seen before! "Upcoming" is a weekly Japanese Internet show that gives you an intimate look at how Japanese music groups work to put recordings together and perform for their fans. The show is hosted by singers Takeshi Matsubara, Marina Okada (of the group LoVendo) and Moemi Hasegawa (of Bitter & Sweet).
imdb.title: Upcoming
plot: See the backstage prep of music concerts and what goes into the recording of a new song like you've never seen before! "_Upcoming_ (qv)" is a weekly Japanese Internet show that gives you an intimate look at how Japanese music groups work to put recordings together and perform for their fans. The show is hosted by singers Takeshi Matsubara, Marina Okada (of the group LoVendo) and Moemi Hasegawa (of Bitter & Sweet).
